call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Harden's (LAC) pass goes out of bounds.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) brings his hands toward Tucker (LAC) and marginal contact occurs as Caldwell-Pope establishes in his path.
Tucker (LAC) initiates illegal contact with Jokic's (DEN) arm in the post.
Tucker (LAC) is assessed an unsportsmanlike technical foul.
Zubac (LAC) firms up over his right foot in Braun's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Braun (DEN) initiates contact with Zubac's (LAC) arm that impedes his ability to pursue the rebound.
Zubac (LAC) initiates contact to Jokic's (DEN) wrist, affecting his shot attempt in the post.
Jokic (DEN) attempts to go for the steal and initiates contact with Zubac's (LAC) arm, causing him to lose control of the ball.
Braun (DEN) leans to his right, but the contact with Zubac (LAC) is marginal.
Gordon (DEN) avoids making contact with Zubac's (LAC) arm during his shot attempt near the rim.
Gordon (DEN) maintains his hand on the side of the ball and does not bring any part of his hand underneath the ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Gordon (DEN) loses his footing and is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Braun (DEN) legally contests Harden's (LAC) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Jokic (DEN) and Zubac (LAC) mutually engage during the rebound.
Gordon (DEN) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Tucker (LAC) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
